Before beginning work on any project, it's usually a good idea to know what you're building.
-Below is a basic list of things we want our users to be able to do:
  -Create new posts
  -View all posts ordered by upvotes
  -Add comments about a given post
  -View comments for a given post
  -Upvote posts and comments

Steps
-start with the Angular side of things
-AngularJS is a frontend framework developed by Google with the goal of making single page web applications easier to build, test, and maintain
